Key Match Events: Mexico equalize in 11th minute of stoppage time
Mexico triumph in penalties to book Copa America spot
Luis Chavez scored in the second half
Edson Alvarez scored the equalizer in stoppage time
Bryan Rochez's penalty was stopped by Luis Malagon
Edrick Menjivar stopped Cesar Huerta's penalty twice but was deemed off his line both times
Post-Match Reflections: Edson Alvarez was praised for his crucial goal and performance
Honduras were disappointed and felt unlucky with the outcome
Mexico secured a spot in the Copa America and will face Panama in the Nations League semifinals
Honduras will face Costa Rica in March to determine their Copa America fate
